<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Brutalist — Lakecia Gunter</title>
<style>
  :root{--yellow:#f7e019;--black:#0a0a0a;--white:#ffffff}
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0}
  body{background:var(--yellow);color:var(--black);font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;line-height:1.4;font-size:16px}
  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
  img{max-width:100%;display:block;border:4px solid var(--black)}
  
  .nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:16px 20px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;border-bottom:4px solid var(--black);position:relative}
  .brand{font-size:18px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em}
  .nav-links{display:flex;gap:24px}
  .nav-links a{text-decoration:underline}
  .nav-links a:hover{text-decoration:none}
  .menu-toggle{display:block !important;background:none;border:none;font-size:28px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:700}
  
  
    .menu-toggle{display:block}
    .nav-links{display:none;position:absolute;top:100%;left:0;right:0;background:var(--yellow);padding:20px;border-bottom:4px solid var(--black);flex-direction:column;gap:16px;z-index:100}
    .nav-links.active{display:flex}
  }
  
  .hero{padding:40px 20px;border-bottom:4px solid var(--black)}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(40px,9vw,100px);line-height:.85;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin-bottom:20px}
  .hero p{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:28px;max-width:700px}
  .button{display:inline-block;background:var(--black);color:var(--yellow);padding:16px 28px;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;text-transform:uppercase;border:4px solid var(--black);cursor:pointer}
  .button:hover{background:var(--yellow);color:var(--black)}
  
  .section{padding:40px 20px;border-bottom:4px solid var(--black)}
  .section h2{font-size:clamp(32px,6vw,64px);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:.9;margin-bottom:24px}
  .section p{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px;max-width:800px}
  .section p strong{font-weight:700;background:var(--black);color:var(--yellow);padding:2px 6px}
  
  .services-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0}
  .service-box{border:4px solid var(--black);padding:32px;margin:-2px}
  .service-box h3{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px}
  .service-box p{font-size:16px;font-weight:700}
  
  .cta-section{background:var(--black);color:var(--yellow);padding:60px 20px}
  .cta-section h2{font-size:clamp(40px,8vw,90px);font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:.85;margin-bottom:20px}
  .cta-section p{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:32px;max-width:600px}
  .cta-section .button{background:var(--yellow);color:var(--black);border-color:var(--yellow)}
  .cta-section .button:hover{background:var(--black);color:var(--yellow)}
  
  .footer{padding:20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;border-top:4px solid var(--black)}
  
  
    .services-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .footer{flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="wrap">
  <nav class="nav">
    <a href="/shotgun-12/v5-brutalist/" class="brand">LAKECIA GUNTER</a>
    <button class="menu-toggle" onclick="document.querySelector('.nav-links').classList.toggle('active')">&#9776;</button>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/shotgun-12/v5-brutalist/">HOME</a>
      <a href="/shotgun-12/v5-brutalist/about/">ABOUT</a>
      <a href="/shotgun-12/v5-brutalist/services/">SERVICES</a>
      <a href="/shotgun-12/v5-brutalist/contact/">CONTACT</a>
    </div>
  </nav>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <header class="hero">
    <h1>AI IS CHANGING EVERYTHING. DON'T GET LEFT BEHIND.</h1>
    <p>Former Microsoft CTO. 25 years from DoD to Fortune 50. Now helping women leaders win with AI.</p>
    <a href="/shotgun-12/v5-brutalist/contact/" class="button">BOOK FREE CALL</a>
  </header>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <section class="section">
    <h2>MOST AI CONSULTING IS BUILT BY MEN. FOR MEN.</h2>
    <p>They talk about <strong>prompt engineering</strong> like it's rocket science. They sell <strong>fear</strong> dressed up as strategy. They build tools for productivity, not <strong>power</strong>.</p>
    <p>Women leaders don't need another dashboard. They need <strong>judgment</strong>. They need someone who has sat in the rooms where billion-dollar decisions get made and can translate that fluency into <strong>their</strong> context.</p>
    <p>That's what I do. No jargon. No panic. Just <strong>clarity and leverage</strong>.</p>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <section class="section">
    <h2>WHAT I DO</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-box">
        <h3>AI STRATEGY FOR BOARDS</h3>
        <p>Help your board understand AI risk, opportunity, and governance in plain language they can act on.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-box">
        <h3>EXECUTIVE AI COACHING</h3>
        <p>One-on-one coaching for women executives adopting AI. Build confidence, cut through hype.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-box">
        <h3>AI IMPLEMENTATION SPRINTS</h3>
        <p>2-4 week hands-on sprints to get your team using AI tools that actually move the needle.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-box">
        <h3>WOMEN'S AI LEADERSHIP CIRCLE</h3>
        <p>Small cohort of women leaders navigating AI together. Monthly sessions, peer support.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>READY TO LEAD?</h2>
    <p>Book a free 30-minute AI strategy call. No pitch, just clarity.</p>
    <a href="/shotgun-12/v5-brutalist/contact/" class="button">BOOK YOUR CALL</a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <footer class="footer">
    <span>LAKECIA GUNTER / AI FOR WOMEN LEADERS</span>
    <span><a href="/shotgun-12/v5-brutalist/contact/">CONTACT</a></span>
  </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>